description: Philip is back, and Kellin breaks him in! They played some soccer to break the ice, but really didn’t need that – they got along right from the get-go, as if they’ve been friends for a while. “I think we both love soccer balls, you know?” Kellin smirked. Philip admired Kellin’s body, and couldn’t wait to get pounded. Kellin showed the newbie how it’s done around here, and Philip just submitted to the pleasure!
title: Kellin & Philip: Bareback
